data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
If no figure is selected: "+" - zooms in on the whole image. "-" - decreases the scale of the whole image. Up Arrow Key - move the whole image up. Down Arrow Key - move the whole image down. Right Arrow Key - moves the entire image to the right. Left Arrow Key - moves the entire image to the left.
If a figure is selected: "+" - zooms in on the selected figure. "-" - zooms out the selected figure. Up Arrow Key - moves the selected figure up. Down Arrow Key - moves the selected figure down. Right Arrow Key - moves the selected figure to the right. Left Arrow Key - moves the selected shape to the left.
